      "Leo's spiritual path is one of discovering that the divine light they seek externally has always been burning within them. Their spiritual archetype is the Sacred Sovereign — the king or queen who rules not through force but through the radiance of their own fully realized being. Leo finds the divine through creation, through beauty, through the act of bringing something magnificent into existence that did not exist before. They are natural channels for creative spirit, and their art — in whatever form it takes — is their most potent spiritual practice. Leo also encounters the sacred through love: through the giving and receiving of deep, genuine, heart-centered connection. For Leo, the spiritual journey involves a profound shift from performing for approval to expressing from authenticity, from needing to be the center to choosing to be the Sun — giving light freely, unconditionally, without requiring anything in return.",

